OL,3,CNewport's oldest fish and chip shop
OL,4,Cgoes on the market
OL,6,FThe culinary landscape of Newport is
OL,7,Fset to change as one of the city's
OL,8,Fmost iconic fish and chip shops has
OL,9,Fgone up for sale.
OL,11,FVacara's fish and chip shop has been
OL,12,Fput on the market after almost 135
OL,13,Fyears of being in the city.
OL,15,FThe current owner, Alan Edwards, is
OL,16,Fthe great-grandson of the shop's
OL,17,Ffounders, who opened their first shop
OL,18,Fin 1888.
