OL,3,CNewport's oldest fish and chip shop
OL,4,Cgoes on the market
OL,6,FHe says he'll be sad to shut up the
OL,7,Fshop for the last time, but he hopes
OL,8,Fthe right person will keep it going
OL,9,Ffor another century.
OL,11,FIt has been the mainstay of Newport
OL,12,FCity Centre for 135 years, but Alan
OL,13,Fand his predecessor have had to deal
OL,14,Fwith their fair share of obstacles
OL,15,Falong the way.
OL,17,FAlan said his great-grandparents first
OL,18,Fopened Vacara's not far from Newport's
OL,19,FSt Pauls Church, in 1888. "They opened
OL,20,Fa wet fish shop", Alan said.
