OL,3,CNewport's oldest fish and chip shop
OL,4,Cgoes on the market
OL,6,F"But it seemed to be that frying fish
OL,7,Fwas catching on in the UK, so they
OL,8,Fdecided to fry".
OL,10,FHowever, soon after they decided to
OL,11,Fstart frying fish, Alan explained his
OL,12,Frelatives hit problems; the
OL,13,Fcongregation of the nearby church
OL,14,Fcomplained about the smell coming from
OL,15,Fthe chippy.
OL,17,F"They raised this with the local
OL,18,Fauthority who then decided to fine
OL,19,Fthem a shilling a day, until they
OL,20,Fmoved operations", he added.
