OL,3,CNewport's oldest fish and chip shop
OL,4,Cgoes on the market
OL,6,FThe Vacaras temporarily moved the shop
OL,7,Fto Pill in Newport, before settling on
OL,8,Fthe site where they are now, in 1900.
OL,10,FFast forward a few decades, Alan says
OL,11,Fthe pandemic was a recent bump in the
OL,12,Froad for Vacaras.
OL,14,F"Since the pandemic, it has been
OL,15,Fdifficult: we don't see people after 5
OL,16,Fpm anymore - the town goes quiet", he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"I'll be sad (to close) - I've still
OL,20,Fgot plenty of energy but you just
OL,21,Fdon't know what's going to happen.
