OL,3,CNewport's oldest fish and chip shop
OL,4,Cgoes on the market
OL,6,F"There comes a time when you want to
OL,7,Fnot take any chances", he added.
OL,9,F"I'm seventy-six next month and life
OL,10,Fgets physically more challenging -
OL,11,Fit's sad to have to eventually either
OL,12,Fclose the business altogether or
OL,13,Factually have someone come in who
OL,14,Fwould actually want to carry on in
OL,15,Fthis kind of arrangement."
OL,17,FRegular customers are sad to see Alan
OL,18,Fgo.
OL,20,F"It's always good", one said.
