OL,3,CNewport's oldest fish and chip shop
OL,4,Cgoes on the market
OL,6,F"The chips have always been
OL,7,Fexceptional and, you get a small piece
OL,8,Fof fish and it's enormous, especially
OL,9,Ffor me!", they added.
OL,11,FAnother said she comes to the shop
OL,12,Fevery time she goes to Newport.
OL,14,FAfter spending his life working at the
OL,15,Fshop, Alan has learnt a lot about his
OL,16,Fcustomers. Most importantly - what is
OL,17,FNewport's favourite order?
OL,19,FThe answer: "The Newport money is on
OL,20,Fchip cheese and gravy", according to
OL,21,FAlan.
